  <scopecontent id="aspace_2db8b2c0337c1eb1701dd658e7c9230d">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Items related to the inauguration of Ronald Reagan as President and George Bush as Vice President include tickets, passes, and invitations to inauguration ceremonies and activities; programs; parking signs; photographs; pro-Equal Rights Amendment items; brochures of commemorative items; and religious tracts and magazines.</p><p> Also, clippings and articles concerning various Cornell alumni.</p>  </scopecontent>
